    "description": "Founded in 1995, CPA Roofing & Construction, LLC has spent nearly three decades building a reputation for honesty, reliability, and exceptional craftsmanship throughout Missouri. Based in Warrenton and serving communities across central and eastern Missouri, we've become the trusted contractor of choice for homeowners and businesses who demand quality work and dependable service.\n\nWe specialize in comprehensive roofing and construction solutions, including residential and commercial roofing, siding, drywall, and insurance-based storm restoration. Our deep understanding of insurance claims processes means we're not just contractors — we're advocates who help our clients navigate the complexities of storm damage recovery and ensure they receive the support they deserve.\n\nFrom the first consultation to final inspection, we're committed to transparent communication, meticulous craftsmanship, and standing behind every project we complete. Available seven days a week, fully licensed and insured, and dedicated to protecting your property with work built to last, CPA Roofing & Construction delivers the quality and reliability that Missouri families have trusted since 1995.",
